cast.overview: A knight framed for a tragic crime teams with a scrappy, shape-shifting teen to prove his innocence.
cast.title: Nimona

details.biography: Eugene Lee Yang (born January 18, 1986)  is an Asian-American filmmaker, actor, producer, author, director, activist and internet celebrity, best known for being one-fourth of the YouTube group The Try Guys (2014–present) and his work with BuzzFeed. Yang is also known for his work with various human rights and LGBTQ+ advocacy charities such as The Trevor Project. He is a founding member of 2ND TRY, the Try Guys official independent media company, established alongside Ned Fulmer, Keit Habersberger and Zach Kornfeld.
details.name: Eugene Lee Yang
